'''唐納·紐康伯'''（{{lang-en|Donald Newcombe}}，{{bd|1926年|6月14日|2019年|2月19日|catIdx=Newcombe}}），綽號「紐克」，為美國職棒大聯盟的投手。生涯前期在黑人聯盟，後來加入道奇、紅腿/紅人與印地安人等隊，甚至還效力過日職的中日龍隊。

紐康伯是第一位在職業生涯囊括新人王、年度MVP與賽揚獎的球員。大聯盟也一直到2011年才又有第二位選手達成此成就。而紐康伯在1949年也成為史上第一位於世界大賽出場的黑人選手。1951年，他拿下單季20勝為黑人選手首位。<ref>''Great Baseball Feats, Facts and Figures'', 2008 Edition, p.198, David Nemec and Scott Flatow, A Signet Book, Penguin Group, New York, {{ISBN|978-0-451-22363-0}}</ref>1956年，他成為史上第一位同年拿下賽揚獎與年度MVP的選手。<ref>''Great Baseball Feats, Facts and Figures'', 2008 Edition, p.152, David Nemec and Scott Flatow, A Signet Book, Penguin Group, New York, {{ISBN|978-0-451-22363-0}}</ref>

紐康伯雖然是名投手，不過他的打擊實力相當出色。生涯打擊率為2成71，並敲出15轟。在當時常常以代打身分上場打擊無數次，在當時對於投手來說是很罕見的情形。<ref name="Seidel2002">{{cite book|author=Michael Seidel|title=Streak: Joe Dimaggio and the Summer Of '41|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=zn7tncnFGbwC&pg=PA126|date=March 1, 2002|publisher=U of Nebraska Press|isbn=0-8032-9293-7|pages=126–}}</ref>

==職業生涯==
1944年和1945年，紐康伯在黑人聯盟短暫出賽幾場比賽後，便與道奇簽下合約。他和捕手[[羅伊·坎潘奈拉|羅伊·坎潘奈拉]]成為美國20世紀第一批在大聯盟體系球隊出賽的黑人球員。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=127884015 |title=Holman Stadium Hosted First Interracial Team |publisher=NPR |date=June 16, 2010 |accessdate=February 19, 2019 |archive-date=2019-02-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190220062926/https://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=127884015 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1949年5月20日，紐康伯成為第三位登上大聯盟的非裔美國籍投手。<ref name=sabr>{{cite web|url=https://sabr.org/bioproj/person/a79b94f3|title=Don Newcombe - Society for American Baseball Research|website=sabr.org|accessdate=February 19, 2019|archive-date=2019-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190220024708/https://sabr.org/bioproj/person/a79b94f3|dead-url=no}}</ref>當時他在黑人聯盟球隊的總教練在紐康伯拿下17勝後便馬上與道奇隊談妥合約事宜。<ref name="Cooperstown_Simons">{{cite book|title=The Cooperstown Symposium on Baseball and American Culture, 2000|editor=Alvin L. Hall|isbn=978-0786411207|publisher=McFarland & Company, Inc.|location=Jefferson, North Carolina|last=Simons|first=William M.|date=October 2, 2015|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=OT2oXO8-5KwC&q=larry+dobby+effa+manley+bill+veeck+contract&pg=PA288|access-date=2020-11-25|archive-date=2021-03-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210311033755/https://books.google.com/books?id=OT2oXO8-5KwC&q=larry+dobby+effa+manley+bill+veeck+contract&pg=PA288|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{rp|p.288}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.latimes.com/sports/dodgers/dodgersnow/la-sp-dn-20-greatest-dodgers-kirk-gibson-20150511-story.html|title=The 20 greatest Dodgers of all time, No. 17: Don Newcombe|first=Houston|last=Mitchell|website=latimes.com|accessdate=February 19, 2019|archive-date=2020-02-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200218114929/https://www.latimes.com/sports/dodgers/dodgersnow/la-sp-dn-20-greatest-dodgers-kirk-gibson-20150511-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>他也在大聯盟第一年幫助球隊打進世界大賽。1949年，他和[[傑基·羅賓森|傑基·羅賓森]]、[[羅伊·坎潘奈拉|羅伊·坎潘奈拉]]、Larry Doby成為第一批入選明星賽的黑人球員。紐康伯也在那年拿下新人王。1950年和1951年，他分別拿下19勝與20勝，並在1951年拿下三振王。<ref name="Swaine2009">{{cite book|author=Rick Swaine|title=The Integration of Major League Baseball: A Team by Team History|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=e7Eznt0V6QEC&pg=PA238|date=June 8, 2009|publisher=McFarland|isbn=978-0-7864-5334-4|pages=238–}}</ref>那年道奇與巨人在爭奪國聯冠軍，結果紐康伯在最後一場比賽被總教練換下，由Ralph Branca登板救援。結果巨人隊的[[巴比·湯森|巴比·湯森]]敲出再見全壘打，成功闖進世界大賽。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/11/23/sports/baseball/ralph-branca-who-gave-up-shot-heard-round-the-world-dies-at-90.html |title=Ralph Branca, Who Gave Up 'Shot Heard Round the World,' Dies at 90 - The New York Times |work=Nytimes.com |date= |accessdate=February 19, 2019 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108115927/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/11/23/sports/baseball/ralph-branca-who-gave-up-shot-heard-round-the-world-dies-at-90.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1952年和1953年，紐康伯因為韓戰爆發加入美軍服役。1954年才回歸大聯盟，並拿下9勝8敗，防禦率4.55。但是他隔年強勢拿下20勝5敗，防禦率3.20。該年道奇隊成功拿下隊史首冠。1956年，紐康伯投出了職業生涯最棒的一季。該年他拿下27勝7敗，防禦率3.06。拿下18次完投與5次完封，成為第一屆賽揚獎的得主。然而他在世界大賽卻被洋基隊的[[尤吉·貝拉|尤吉·貝拉]]敲出3發全壘打—他在第二場被貝拉敲出滿貫砲，第七場又被他敲出雙響砲。最後洋基4勝3敗拿下世界大賽冠軍。<ref name=sabr/>

1958年，道奇隊搬到洛杉磯。結果紐康伯像是水土不服一樣，開季吞下0勝6敗。最後他在球季中被交易至紅人，換來Steve Bilko、Johnny Klippstein以及兩名日後指定球員。<ref name=sabr/>合計他在紅人隊拿下24勝21敗，1960年季中，他被交易到印地安人。他在拿下2勝3敗後被球隊釋出，也結束了他的大聯盟生涯。許多人都認為紐康伯是因為酒精成癮才會導致成績大幅度衰退。<ref>{{cite web |last=Scannell |first=Nancy |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/archive/sports/1977/05/22/newcombes-biggest-victory-was-over-the-bottle/b4b9934c-4e4a-4d58-96fe-8dd188da73ab/ |title=Newcombe's Biggest Victory Was Over the Bottle |work=The Washington Post |date=May 22, 1977 |accessdate=February 19, 2019 |archive-date=2020-05-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200514123123/https://www.washingtonpost.com/archive/sports/1977/05/22/newcombes-biggest-victory-was-over-the-bottle/b4b9934c-4e4a-4d58-96fe-8dd188da73ab/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1962年5月28日，紐康伯遠赴東洋加盟日職的中日龍隊。不過他幾乎以外野手和一壘手身分上場，並只投過一場球。該年他出賽81場比賽，打擊率為2成62，並敲出12轟與43分打點。<ref>[https://www.baseball-reference.com/japan/player.cgi?id=newcom001don "Don Newcombe,"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/japan/player.cgi?id=newcom001don |date=20150402105248 }} Baseball-Reference.com. Accessed March 15, 2015.</ref>

紐康伯生涯合計拿下149勝90敗，防禦率3.56，並送出1129次三振。另外他曾在1955年敲出7轟，<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/teams/BRO/1955.shtml |title=1955 Brooklyn Dodgers Statistics |publisher=Baseball-Reference.com |date=January 1, 1970 |accessdate=February 19, 2019 |archive-date=2020-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205110526/https://www.baseball-reference.com/teams/BRO/1955.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>生涯打擊率2成71為投手史上第9高。<ref>{{cite web |author=Omnisport Updated at 2:24 p.m. ET Updated at 2:24 p.m. ET |url=http://www.sportingnews.com/us/mlb/news/don-newcombe-obit-obituary-mlb-brooklyn-dodgers-los-angeles/97xt7u5k0eu314bnmdqyzdf9y |title=Don Newcombe, star pitcher linked to Dodgers' Brooklyn past, dies at 92 | MLB |publisher=Sporting News |date= |accessdate=February 19, 2019 |archive-date=2019-04-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190405105559/http://www.sportingnews.com/us/mlb/news/don-newcombe-obit-obituary-mlb-brooklyn-dodgers-los-angeles/97xt7u5k0eu314bnmdqyzdf9y |dead-url=no }}</ref>
==退休之後==
1970年代晚期，紐康伯成為道奇隊的事務總監。2009年3月，他成為隊上的主席特殊顧問。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/content/printer_friendly/la/y2009/m03/d23/c4055002.jsp|title=Don Newcombe named Special Advisor to the Chairman|work=MLB.com|date=March 23, 2009|accessdate=February 19, 2019|archive-date=2019-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190220063134/http://mlb.mlb.com/content/printer_friendly/la/y2009/m03/d23/c4055002.jsp|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2016年，他入選了棒球文物館(Baseball Reliquary)裡的永恆之殿(Shrine of the Eternals)。<ref name="BRSOTE Inductees">[http://www.baseballreliquary.org/awards/shrine-of-the-eternals/shrine-of-the-eternals-electees "Shrine of the Eternals – Inductees"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.baseballreliquary.org/awards/shrine-of-the-eternals/shrine-of-the-eternals-electees |date=20200919092503 }}. Baseball Reliquary. Retrieved 2019-08-14.</ref>
==個人生活==
紐康伯一生有過3段婚姻，他分別在1960年和1994年與他的前兩任妻子離婚。<ref name=sabr/><ref>{{cite web|last=Marino |first=David |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/obituaries/don-newcombe-pitching-star-who-later-led-programs-to-treat-substance-abuse-dies-at-92/2019/02/19/3c7e774e-3479-11e9-a400-e481bf264fdc_story.html?noredirect=on |title=Don Newcombe, pitching star who later led programs to treat substance abuse, dies at 92 |work=The Washington Post |date= |accessdate=February 19, 2019}}</ref>

在職業生涯末期，紐康伯患上了酒精成癮。他還為了買酒喝典當了他的世界大賽冠軍戒。1966年，在他妻子以離婚作為威脅的情況下，紐康伯終於戒酒成功。他也利用他的自身經驗幫助許多人遠離藥物濫用的問題，包含他的前隊友[[毛利·威爾斯|毛利·威爾斯]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://articles.latimes.com/1990-01-31/sports/sp-1151_1_maury-wills/2|title=For Wills, Basepaths Led to His Own Private Hell : Baseball: After battling drugs and depression, the former Dodger shortstop finally feels part of a team--and important as an individual|first=Maryann|last=Hudson|work=Los Angeles Times|date=January 31, 1990|accessdate=February 19, 2019}}</ref>

2010年，參議員[[芭芭拉·柏克瑟|芭芭拉·柏克瑟]]舉了一場募款活動。當時紐康伯和時任美國總統歐巴馬都有到場。當時歐巴馬還曾說過一句話<ref>{{citation | last=Obama | first=Barack | author-link=Barack Obama | title=Remarks by the President at fundraising event for Senator Boxer and the DNC | date=April 19, 2010 | url=https://obamawhitehouse.archives.gov/the-press-office/remarks-president-fundraising-event-senator-boxer-and-dnc | accessdate=September 12, 2017 | archive-date=2020-09-18 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200918133745/https://obamawhitehouse.archives.gov/the-press-office/remarks-president-fundraising-event-senator-boxer-and-dnc | dead-url=no }}</ref> ：
<blockquote>
''要是沒有[[傑基·羅賓森|羅賓森]]和紐康伯的努力，我現在不會成為美國總統。'' 
:- 巴拉克·歐巴馬, 2010年4月19日.</blockquote>

2019年2月19日，紐康伯因病去世，享壽92歲。他最後被安葬在洛杉磯國家公墓裡。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Perry |first1=Dayn |title=Don Newcombe, former Dodgers great and inaugural Cy Young Award winner, dead at 92 |url=https://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/don-newcombe-former-dodgers-great-and-inaugural-cy-young-award-winner-dead-at-92/ |website=CBS Sports |accessdate=February 19, 2019 |archive-date=2019-02-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190220120359/https://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/don-newcombe-former-dodgers-great-and-inaugural-cy-young-award-winner-dead-at-92/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>
